<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-971f54ae-9e4c-42f0-bf95-d5c960e98209'>
            
<p class="">1.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-7e018c26-674a-4cf1-8b6f-1e0ca6d21c42">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-7e018c26-674a-4cf1-8b6f-1e0ca6d21c42">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-7e018c26-674a-4cf1-8b6f-1e0ca6d21c42">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-7e018c26-674a-4cf1-8b6f-1e0ca6d21c42">
                Mr. Ronald Chamberlain
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-7e018c26-674a-4cf1-8b6f-1e0ca6d21c42" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-12-05/debates/d6e02175-3b25-43f8-a0dc-2619de9af737/ShipRepairs(ForeignYards)#contribution-7e018c26-674a-4cf1-8b6f-1e0ca6d21c42">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Minister of Transport whether he will now take action to prevent British-registered ships from being sent abroad for refitting and repair while unemployment persists at its present level in British ship-repairing yards.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-7e018c26-674a-4cf1-8b6f-1e0ca6d21c42" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-12-05/debates/d6e02175-3b25-43f8-a0dc-2619de9af737/ShipRepairs(ForeignYards)#contribution-7e018c26-674a-4cf1-8b6f-1e0ca6d21c42">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-9ab8c6ba-275f-43d0-80c0-b928a74077b4">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-9ab8c6ba-275f-43d0-80c0-b928a74077b4">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-9ab8c6ba-275f-43d0-80c0-b928a74077b4">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-9ab8c6ba-275f-43d0-80c0-b928a74077b4">
                The Parliamentary Secretary to the Ministry of Transport (Mr. James Callaghan)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-9ab8c6ba-275f-43d0-80c0-b928a74077b4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-12-05/debates/d6e02175-3b25-43f8-a0dc-2619de9af737/ShipRepairs(ForeignYards)#contribution-9ab8c6ba-275f-43d0-80c0-b928a74077b4">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">No, Sir. It sometimes saves very valuable ship's time to repair in an overseas port. The policy proposed would hamper the ability of our ships in competition with the ships of other flags to make their full contribution to our national balance of payments.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-9ab8c6ba-275f-43d0-80c0-b928a74077b4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-12-05/debates/d6e02175-3b25-43f8-a0dc-2619de9af737/ShipRepairs(ForeignYards)#contribution-9ab8c6ba-275f-43d0-80c0-b928a74077b4">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-335b9823-0828-44d6-8ee3-e0b522f919e9">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-335b9823-0828-44d6-8ee3-e0b522f919e9">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-335b9823-0828-44d6-8ee3-e0b522f919e9">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-335b9823-0828-44d6-8ee3-e0b522f919e9">
                Mr. Chamberlain
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-335b9823-0828-44d6-8ee3-e0b522f919e9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-12-05/debates/d6e02175-3b25-43f8-a0dc-2619de9af737/ShipRepairs(ForeignYards)#contribution-335b9823-0828-44d6-8ee3-e0b522f919e9">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">While undoubtedly there has to be some further deflation of this industry, is my hon. Friend aware that the position is being greatly aggravated by the despatch to north European ports and to American ports of British ships for repair and refitting, which is being done at cut prices compared with British prices, and will he use his powers to do something about it?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-335b9823-0828-44d6-8ee3-e0b522f919e9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-12-05/debates/d6e02175-3b25-43f8-a0dc-2619de9af737/ShipRepairs(ForeignYards)#contribution-335b9823-0828-44d6-8ee3-e0b522f919e9">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-8c50c6d7-d22a-4de7-acbb-9f3e25845b40">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-8c50c6d7-d22a-4de7-acbb-9f3e25845b40">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-8c50c6d7-d22a-4de7-acbb-9f3e25845b40">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-8c50c6d7-d22a-4de7-acbb-9f3e25845b40">
                Mr. Callaghan
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-8c50c6d7-d22a-4de7-acbb-9f3e25845b40" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-12-05/debates/d6e02175-3b25-43f8-a0dc-2619de9af737/ShipRepairs(ForeignYards)#contribution-8c50c6d7-d22a-4de7-acbb-9f3e25845b40">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">No, Sir; I do not think it is the case that the position is being seriously aggravated. My hon. Friend will remember that this is a two-way traffic, with foreign ships being repaired in this country as well as British ships being repaired abroad, and that sometimes the balance of advantage is on our side.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-8c50c6d7-d22a-4de7-acbb-9f3e25845b40" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-12-05/debates/d6e02175-3b25-43f8-a0dc-2619de9af737/ShipRepairs(ForeignYards)#contribution-8c50c6d7-d22a-4de7-acbb-9f3e25845b40">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
